## Require (verb-specific)

- **(N-R1)** Actuator output schema = mechanical spec (vertex topology + state cycle + binding affinity + pose group). **Canonical schema**: `nanobot/spec/actuator_output_v1.schema.json` (raw_77_nanobot_actuation_v2). Required fields: `vertex_decorations` (12 entries: vertex_id, ligand, charge_e, mass_amu), `pose_canonical_form` (representative_pose 0..23, orbit_size=24, stabilizer_order), `state_cycle` (4-state S0..S3 + 4×4 transition rate matrix in s⁻¹), `binding_affinity` (per-ligand K_d_M, k_on_M_s, k_off_s). Cycle 26 task: extend `nanobot_actuation_simulation.py` to emit v2 schema; v1 (cycle 24) emits only `pose_canonicalize_speedup_factor=24.0` without canonical pose representative.
- **(N-R2)** Sister-axis 분담 (C0a 결과 2026-05-05 — F-NB-5 **PARTIAL**, audit verdict COLLISION): hexa-bio NANOBOT = single-molecule **architectural primitive** (atoms-level, 4-state motor kinetics, 12-vertex skeleton, kT thermal floor 310K, L0-L6); `life/therapeutic-nanobot/` = integrated **clinical-application system** (drug loading, immune evasion, biodistribution, targeting ligands, L7-L9). Cross-domain handshake: hexa-bio NANOBOT emits L6 single-machine witness; therapeutic-nanobot consumes as propulsion subsystem 추가로 clinical layer composition. **hexa-bio L6 emission schema (this repo)**: `nanobot/spec/handoff_l6_emission_v0.schema.json` (raw_77_nanobot_l6_handoff_v1). Fields: `{actuator_id, n6_invariant {sigma_6, tau_6, phi_6, J2}, work_per_cycle_kT, vertex_decorations, pose_canonical_form, brownian_collapse_detected, l6_layer="single_machine_kinetics", expected_consumer_layers=[L7_drug_load, L8_immune_evasion, L9_biodistribution], joint_witness_path="design/kick/2026-05-28_hexa-nanobot-therapeutic-nanobot-boundary.json"}`. `emission_blocked_until_schema_lock=true` (v0). **Out-of-repo dependency**: `~/core/n6-architecture/domains/life/therapeutic-nanobot/therapeutic-nanobot.md` §3/§11 에 hexa-nanobot 선등록 (2026-04-28) acknowledgment 추가 + therapeutic-nanobot acceptance schema (raw_77_therapeutic_nanobot_l7_acceptance_v1, fields TBD by canonical repo) + joint handshake witness JSON (`design/kick/2026-05-28_hexa-nanobot-therapeutic-nanobot-boundary.json`) 발행 — n6-architecture 프로젝트에서 처리. **F-NB-5 full PASS = 위 작업 완료 후.**
- **(N-R3)** Meta `.roadmap.hexa_bio` §E (R1-R8) 전 도메인 Require 상속

